ers of livestock concerning the existence of a lien or security interest against livestock and to submit a report to Congress not later than "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1979-02-01"},"text":"Feb. 1, 1979","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
